2022 Brazilian Thoracic Association recommendations for long-term home oxygen 
therapy.

Castellano MVCO(1), Pereira LFF(2), Feitosa PHR(3), Knorst MM(4)(5), Salim 
C(6)(7), Rodrigues MM(1), Ferreira EVM(8), Duarte RLM(9), Togeiro SM(10), 
Stanzani LZL(3), Medeiros Júnior P(6), Schelini KNM(11), Coelho LS(12), Sousa 
TLF(13), Almeida MB(14), Alvarez AE(15).

Author information:
(1). Hospital do Servidor Público Estadual de São Paulo - IAMSPE - São Paulo 
(SP) Brasil.
(2). Hospital das Clínicas, Universidade Federal de Minas Gerais - UFMG - Belo 
