Interleukin-6 initiates muscle- and adipose tissue wasting in a novel C57BL/6 
model of cancer-associated cachexia.

Pototschnig I(1), Feiler U(1), Diwoky C(1), Vesely PW(2), Rauchenwald T(1), Paar 
M(3), Bakiri L(4), Pajed L(1), Hofer P(1), Kashofer K(2), Sukhbaatar N(5), 
Schoiswohl G(6), Weichhart T(5), Hoefler G(2)(7), Bock C(8)(9), Pichler M(10), 
