Attributable disease burden related to low bone mineral density in Iran from 
1990 to 2019: results from the Global Burden of Disease 2019.

Azangou-Khyavy M(#)(1), Saeedi Moghaddam S(#)(1), Mohammadi E(1)(2), Shobeiri 
P(1), Rashidi MM(1), Ahmadi N(1), Shahsavan S(1), Shirzad Moghaddam Z(1), 
